         <abstract>
            <p><persName ref="#nawazishKhan">Nawazish Khan</persName> instructs the landlord (chaudhri) <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName> and the record-keeper (qanungo) <persName ref="#parasRam">Paras Ram</persName> of district (pargana) <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName> to ensure the continued settlement of people and agricultural lands such that there is an increase of 20-30 percent.</p>
