   <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1659_dai_lns235ms_g_r.jpg"/>

         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>الله اکبر</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div1" corresp="#orig_div1">
            <p>God is great</p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p><stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
               <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">نوازش خان</persName>
               مُرید حضرت
               <persName ref="#shahJahan">شاه جهان</persName>
            </mentioned></stamp></p>
         </div>
         
         <div xml:id="trans_div2" corresp="#orig_div2">
            <p><stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned><persName ref="#nawazishKhan">Nawazish Khan</persName>, disciple of Lord <persName ref="#shahJahan">Shah Jahan</persName></mentioned></stamp>
            </p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>زبده الاقران    
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرسوتم</persName>
               چودهری و
               <persName ref="#parasRam">پرسرام</persName>
               قانونگوی پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">دهار</placeName>
               بعنایت
               <lb/>امیدوار گشته بدانند وقت تردد آبادانی و کشتکار زراعت
               <lb/>همین است باید که درین باب چنان سعی نمایند که از گذشته
               <lb/>ده بیست ده سی ٣٠ تردد آبادانی و کشتکار زراعت بظهور آید
               <lb/>و اگر درینمادة کوتاهی و تغافلی خواهد کرد باز خواست این مقدمه
               <lb/>بعهده آنهاست درین باب نهایت تاکید دانسته از
               <lb/>فرموده تخلف نورزند تحریر فی التاریخ
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri"><num>٨</num>
               ماه رمضان سنه
               <num>۱۰۶۹</num></date>
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div3" corresp="#orig_div3">
            <p>
               <lb/>Eminent among Contemporaries
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam [Das]</persName>
               <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> and
               <persName ref="#parasRam">Paras Ram</persName>
               <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qanungo">qanungo</ref> of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>,
               <lb/>having hoped for kindness, know that this is the time to make efforts for the
               populating and cultivating [of the area] and the husbanding of agriculture.
               <lb/>It is necessary that [<persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName> and <persName ref="#parasRam">Paras Ram</persName>] make such efforts that compared to the past,
               <lb/>an increase of twenty-fold or thirty-fold 30 in the population and agriculture shall become evident.
               <lb/>And if in this matter there is deficiency or negligence, an investigation of this case
               <lb/>is their obligation. Knowing this matter to be an instruction,
               <lb/>do not violate what has been ordered. Written on the <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">8th of the month of Ramzan in the year 1069</date>. <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further</g>. <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further</g>.</p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="right margin">
            <p>هو</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div4" corresp="#orig_div4">
            <p>He [God] is</p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p>
               <lb/>المسطور حسب مقرر شناسند
               <lb/>بموجب فرموده عمل نماید و در کشت و کار
               <lb/>و افزونی زراعت سعی موفوره بحال آورد و
               <lb/>بهبود خود درین داند
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div5" corresp="#orig_div5">
            <p>
               <lb/>[<persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName> and <persName ref="#parasRam">Paras Ram</persName>] should understand this to be confirmed as written.
               <lb/>Execute as ordered. Make serious efforts in the tilling [of the land]
               <lb/>and in improving agriculture.
               <lb/>It is known that their own welfare is in this. <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further</g>. <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further</g>. </p>
         </div>
         
         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1659_dai_lns235ms_g_v.jpg"/>

         <div xml:id="orig_div6" xml:lang="per" type="laterAddition" rend="top centre">
            <p><unclear>نمبر</unclear>
               <num>۶</num></p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div6" xml:id="trans_div6">
